{
  "stem": "20084.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We used to carry them from one-- from-- form one railroad track.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Here was, on the right-hand side, was-- was the railroad track.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we had to carry them and step down to the ground, then on the-- on the left side was another train, where [NON-ENGLISH] was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And you had to carry them up the-- up the stairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "There wasn't a even platform where-- where they-- but taking them down and then carried them on our backs, or when it was a guy was heavy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So two of us were carrying him, and carrying him up, up, up, up, up the stairs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they had a lot of gold and Russian rubles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they had watches that they stole, and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] oh, we could eat something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We could grab a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They-- they-- they wouldn't let us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But there was plenty of food down there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We could eat down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But we couldn't take nothing back home, back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And-- and on one of those-- one in particular guy was a young SS man, blond and blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And he was moaning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Nothing was wrong with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "His feet were frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And he was telling me a story in the little broken Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "So I knew that he was from the border town of Poland, [INAUDIBLE], somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And he was saying to me that he was on the front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And those Russians can stay for days and nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "He was just a few hours and his legs got frozen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And he called me a friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I was so mad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "He was a big guy, maybe six feet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And I grabbed him on my back and dragged him down the stairs and hit with-- with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
